high_descs: Move to the table to the right of you
Pick up a knife from the table
Move over slightly from the current position
Place the knife in a bowl on the table
Pick up the bowl from the table
Move to the counter to the right of the table
Place the bowl on the counter
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a knife on the counter with microwave on it.

high_descs: Turn right, go forward to the rectangular white table.
Take the knife to the left of the tomato from the table.
Stay at the table.
Put the knife in the white bowl on the table.
Take the bowl from the table.
Turn right, go straight, turn left at the stand with the coffee machine.
Put the bowl on the left side of the stand.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a knife on a stand.

high_descs: Turn to your right and face the kitchen table
Pick up a knife off of the table
Look down at the bowl on the table
Drop the knife into the bowl on the table
Pick up the bowl with the knife in it
Move over a step to your right so you are facing the coffee maker
Set the bowl with the knife in it down on the table top
anns.task_desc: Move a bowl with a knife in it
